ion — with scope, boundaries, corpus sources per child\",\"graphEvents\":[{\"type\":\"finding\",\"id\":\"f-iter003-001\",\"label\":\"6 sub-skills proposed: visual, color, motion, layout, a11y, interaction\",\"iteration\":3},{\"type\":\"finding\",\"id\":\"f-iter003-002\",\"label\":\"sk-design-interface naturally evolves into sk-design-visual (rename + expand)\",\"iteration\":3},{\"type\":\"finding\",\"id\":\"f-iter003-003\",\"label\":\"sk-design-md-generator stays as extraction engine, consumed by sk-design-color\",\"iteration\":3},{\"type\":\"finding\",\"id\":\"f-iter003-004\",\"label\":\"Process docs (critique, redesign) are cross-cutting — better as conditional refs than separate sub-skill\",\"iteration\":3},{\"type\":\"finding\",\"id\":\"f-iter003-005\",\"label\":\"taste-skill.md is the richest corpus source (600+ lines) — feeds visual, color, layout, and motion\",\"iteration\":3},{\"type\":\"finding\",\"id\":\"f-iter003-006\",\"label\":\"designer-skills-main interaction-design plugin has 16 skills including cognitive laws (Hicks, Millers, Fitts)\",\"iteration\":3}]}' >> \".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/001-corpus-research/research/lineages/mimo25pro/deep-research-state.jsonl\"","time":{"start":1782387287949,"end":1782387287957}},"id":"prt_efe8fa7880015m0TNIz3yVh5p0","sessionID":"ses_1017781abffe8Jf4LLgGRFccm9","messageID":"msg_efe8f8c48001uOAslo4N7nfh7e"}}
